{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "HC", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient100", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " Οι μαμά και το παιδί, οι δοντάρια, το δοντάρ και το δονταράκι, τρώνε τη σάρκα σαν ένα βούβαλο. Γιατί βούβαλο είναι αυτό.", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "AD", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient115", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " Για δοκιμασία λίγο, το πάσχο που είναι το 10 ευρώ.", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "MCI", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient125", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " Είναι εδώ ένα ζευγάρι από Λιοντάρια που τρώγουνε τώρα αυτό τι, τάρνα, τι είναι, όχι, τι είναι αυτό το πράγμα, ένας ελαφροειδές είναι.", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "MCI", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient126", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " Λοιπόν, έχω την εντύπωση ότι είναι δύο λιοντάρια, ένα μεγάλο και ένα πιο μικρό, ή αρσενικό και θηλυκό. Μάλλον το δεύτερο είναι. Αρσενικός είναι αυτός με τα πολλά και θηλυκό είναι το άλλο χωρίς. Τα οποία έχουν κατά κρυουργής ένα ζώο. Ωραία, μια χαρά.", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "MCI", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient130", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " Ένα λιοντάρι και το λιονταράκι του, το παιδί και... ...και το παιδί και το λιοντάρι του.", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "MCI", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient131", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " 2 λεοντάρια και πάνω σε έναν τάτρα.", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "AD", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient32", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " Ωραία.", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "AD", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient35", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " Αυτό τι βλέπετε. Φιλικά, στην Καρχαρία, το άμμο τι είναι αυτό εδώ με τα δόντια, αυτό το ζώο. Στόμα ανοιγμένο, δεν μπορεί να πω δίπλα, σαν Καρχαρία αυτό ούτε. Εδώ λιονταρίνα με λιοντάρι.", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "MCI", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient36", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " Ακόμα μια φορά γιατί είναι. Πείτε μας. Βλέπω ένα κουφάρι ζώο που τρώνε η λιονταρίνα με το λιοντάρι. Μάλιστα.", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "MCI", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient37", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " Βλέπω ένα λιοντάρι, το οποίο είναι γυρισμένο από το κεφάλι του. Δύο λιοντάρια πρέπει να είναι, ένα μπροστά και ένα πίσω. Αυτό δεν ξέρω. Μάθατε, ωραία. Τι είναι αυτό?", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "MCI", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient38", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " Το αρσενικό λοντάρι φυσικά θα είναι με το μικρό τους και η φωλιά τους. Σπηλιά που μένουν.", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "MCI", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient39", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " Αυτό είναι βιοντάρι σίγουρα. Εδώ είναι άλλο πάλι. Τρία αυτά έχει. Τρία ειδών ζώα στο χώμα.", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
