{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "MCI", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient42", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": "", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "AD", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient43", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " Βλέπω ένα σκύλι εδώ, δεν είναι σκύλι αυτό, αυτό είναι ένα άγριο, αυτό πάει από εδώ πιθυγί, τι είναι αυτό, είναι ένα άγριο ζώο, τι ζώο είναι, δεν μπορείτε να το πείτε. Καλός, καλός, ναι. Και αυτό εδώ είναι, βάρετε αυτό είναι ζώο όλα, τι ζώο είναι, βέβαιο, ναι. Πώς το λένε αυτό, ρε Γιάννη. Ωραία.", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "MCI", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient44", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " είναι μια οικογένεια λονταριών που τρώει ένα ζώο.", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "MCI", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient45", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " Φοράει να φοράει, να φοράει, να φοράει. Καρχαρίες είναι, νεκτάρι και το μικρό κυλεντωράκι και η μάνα. Καρχαρίες είναι αυτός.", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "MCI", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient46", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " Μια λεονταρίνα με το λεονταράκι της. Υπάρχουν κάποιοι που βλέπουν κάτι τρόκανικο.", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "MCI", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient47", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " Ένα αριστερικό λιοντάρι, ένας κύκνος, ένα φυλλικό λιοντάρι και αυτό το τύνι. Τι γνωστή είναι ο Γουράιμ, δεν μπορούμε να το καταλάβουμε.", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "MCI", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient48", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " Εδώ βλέπω τον λοντάρι με το λονταράκι της.", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "MCI", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient49", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " Τα σπίσουλα αυτά, το νεοντάρι είναι αυτό. Νεοντάρι, τίγρε, εδώ κάτω τι είναι. Δεν τα βλέπω. Αυτό τι είναι. Και αυτό, αυτό δεν το ξέρω. Δεν το ξέρω αυτό το ζώο.", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "MCI", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient50", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " ένας γνώκερος μισοφαγωμένος, ένα λιοντάρι και ένα πάθηρας ή κούγκαρα, δεν ξέρω τι είναι.", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "AD", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient53", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " Εδώ είναι μάλλον αυτό, αυτό είναι πάλι ένα ζώο, δεν είναι αυτό όλο και είναι πάνω τους τα άλλα τα ζώα. Αυτό το ζώο τι είναι όμως, σιγά σιγά βλέπω. Αυτά που βλέπετε τι ζώα είναι. Αυτό λύκος, όχι λεοντάρι, λεοντάρι είναι από εδώ, αυτό είναι έτσι το κεφάλι του και αυτό λεοντάρι είναι μήπως. Αλλά τώρα αυτό δεν ξέρω τι είναι εδώ, δεν μπορώ να το δω. Όχι, όχι.", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "MCI", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient54", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " Αχ, βλέπω το λιοντάρι με τη... δυο λιοντάρια πάνω από ένα ψωφίμι. Νόμιζα λιοντάρ και λιονταράκι ήτανε.", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "AD", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient55", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " Ευχαριστώ πολύ. Είναι μελένα μαζί. Πώς το διακοπεί. Δεν μπορώ να διακλίνω. Τι είναι αυτό το πράγμα. Είναι σπηλιά. Είναι κάποιος τερκουαρευτό. Δεν ξέρω τι στον αγώνα σημαίνει.", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
