{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "AD", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient59", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " Υπότιτλοι AUTHORWAVE", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "MCI", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient60", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " Τι βλέπετε σε αυτή την οικότητα? Εγώ βλέπω μία μαμά με το μωρό της, Λιονταρίνα, Λιονταρίνα δεν είναι μία μαμά, η οποία κατασπαράζει ή βοηθάει το παιδί της να μάθει πώς να τρώει. Ωραία!", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "AD", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient61", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " Να δούμε αυτό το ζώο. Αυτό είναι το παιδί, φαίνεται, νοογέννητο. Αυτό είναι λάθος, δεν ξέρω, κάτι διαφορετικό είναι από ότι το βλέπω. Με θυμίζει, αλλά δεν μπορεί να με θυμηθώ. Δεν βλέπω τι έχει εδώ μέσα. Τι είναι, κάλυβα. Να'ρθει, εντάξει.", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "AD", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient62", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " Ένα λιοντάρι με το λιονταράκι που τρώνε ένα ζώο.", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "AD", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient63", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " Έχω μια γελάδα, δύο, μια μικρή και τα δω πού είναι εδώ κάτω. navy", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "AD", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient64", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " Δεν ξέρω τι βλέπετε. Βλέπω... Τι ζωή μου αυτά τώρα... Αυτό κεφάλι είναι. Μάλλον ναι, κεφάλι είναι. Αυτό είναι μοσπάρι. Μοσπάρι στο κεφάλι. Τώρα, αυτό το κεφάλι ανήκει σε αυτό το ζώο. Όχι.", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "AD", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient65", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " Εδώ βλέπω ένα λιοντάρι και τη γρυσσίνη. Βλέπω ένα λιοντάρι και τη γρυσσίνη.", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "AD", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient67", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " Λοιπόν, το λεοντάρι, πιθανόν η μάνα, έχει το λεονταράκι της. Το ταΐζει, τώρα το αφήνει... όχι, δεν το ταΐζει γιατί είναι γεγισμένο. Πάντως το προφυλάσσει. Μάλιστα, ωραία.", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "AD", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient68", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " Εδώ τι είναι αυτό. Παραγράψτε τι βλέπετε στιγμή. Το λεοντάρι είναι με το λεονταράκι. Και αυτό δεν μπορώ να το καταλάβω. Είναι ζώο και αυτό. Ποιο. Μήπως είναι κανένα... Το τρώνε, είναι κτηνωμένο. Ναι. Ωραία. Πολύ ωραία. Μάλιστα.", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
{"PID": "Unknown", "Languages": "el", "MMSE": "Unknown", "Diagnosis": "MCI", "Participants": [], "Dataset": "Unknown", "Modality": "Unknown", "Task": [""], "File_ID": "Patient69", "Media": "Unknown", "Age": "Unknown", "Gender": "Unknown", "Education": "Unknown", "Source": "CHA Dataset", "Continents": "Unknown", "Countries": "Unknown", "Duration": "Unknown", "Location": "Unknown", "Date": "Unknown", "Transcriber": "Unknown", "Moca": "Unknown", "Setting": "Unknown", "Comment": "Unknown", "Text_interviewer_participant": " Πώς έπαιρνε σε αυτή την εικόνα. Το λιοντάρι το αρσενικό με το θηλυκό τρώνε ένα βουβάλι. Ωραία.", "Text_participant": [], "Text_interviewer": []}
